OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day with bright or sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Turning cloudier through the
OL,7,Fafternoon with some outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fby the evening, mostly in the north.
OL,9,FCan be heavy across the Lake District.
OL,10,FFeeling warmer as winds fall light for
OL,11,Fmany.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain continues across the
OL,14,Fnorth overnight as cloud thickens and
OL,15,Flowers across the region. A warm night
OL,16,Fto come but turning breezier by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
