OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudier day on Saturday
OL,6,Fas rain becomes confined to higher
OL,7,Fground. Brighter spells developing in
OL,8,Fthe south in the late afternoon, where
OL,9,Fit'll feel warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure continues to build through
OL,13,Fthe weekend, becoming increasingly
OL,14,Fsettled. Temperatures will climb day
OL,15,Fby day, feeling very warm in the
OL,16,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
